Hinge: hinge plate strong, thick; left valve with one thick, elongate cardinal tooth with roughened surface dorsally, one small elongate posterior lateral tooth with fine tubercles; right valve with one low, elongate cardinal tooth, lateral tooth absent; ligament deeply sunken on a nymph (
Figures 1 B, E
).

